{"tid":1690183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上帝同我講 十二月最啱罷工","createTime":"2019-11-03T07:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T13:34:20.000Z","uid":316491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e6d5f8e0e4d142a6523ec3fe84b1e9bea144f14","tid":1690183,"uid":316491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">打工仔聽著</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十二月成個月尾本來就勁多紅日<br />\n唔爭在月頭<span style=\"color: pink;\">放個大假</span><br />\n咁就可以<span style=\"color: pink;\">唞番成個月</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫你諗埋啦<br />\n有薪假又好無薪假又好<br />\n依幾年大家都辛苦啦<br />\n比自己係屋企享受下自由自在嘅生活唔好？<br />\n日日對住啲閪客 冇話唔係大壓力<br />\n屋企有老婆仔女嘅 成日都話你早出晚歸<br />\n係時候陪下佢哋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學生都聽著<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十二月考試 大部份人都會去考嘅<br />\n但你哋唔係成個月都考架嘛<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">每個人都係文宣嘅一份子</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一日抗爭未成功 一日都唔好比佢停<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ff2d6f365f7412b3b5b9485f52ba3afe04a5eabc","tid":1690183,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"玉帝同我講新年先係"},{"pid":"f21060e2fc27dd1db8b8e2351b347c089488ca26","tid":1690183,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:44:03.000Z","msg":"（求人手置頂）【Twitter戰線】加入共識Channel + 有方法避免Twitter當bot同封帳！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690328</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"544b9466cf722e7d74ed92dc464f95f1ceb20912","tid":1690183,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"唔要 : 推！<br />\n試著說 : 我要罷工！<br />\n將罷工融入日常同口號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要罷工！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人！</span><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}